static building isn't possible as some ffmpeg dependencies in Ubuntu aren't built statically
e.g. libchromaprint

Also, this bug makes it very hard:

https://github.com/rust-lang/pkg-config-rs/issues/102

needed stupid hacks like ln -s /usr /not and then doing search replace in pkgconfig/*.pc

see https://pinboard.in/u:phaedrus424/tabs/401050/ for clues
